---
title: Homestead Chicken Breast Stew with Brown-Butter Irish Champ
description: A comforting stew is always a welcome sight at the dinner table, especially when the weather is chilly! Accompanying this chicken stew is a heap of green onion-studded mashed potatoes, also known as Irish champ. We've amped up the flavour of this mash with a nutty and delicious brown butter!
